Usage: deleteNet [-help] <netName> [-bus <startId:endId>]
                 [-moduleBased <moduleName>]

-help                         # Prints out the command usage
<netName>                     # Name of Net (string, required)
-bus <startId:endId>          # bus bit startId:endId (string, optional)
-moduleBased <moduleName>     # Name of verilog module (string, optional)